{"word":"ἡρῷον","slug":"ἡρῷον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἡρῷον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἥρως'><el>ἥρως</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>the temple</i> or <i>chapel of a hero</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>θἠρῷον</el>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <el>τὸ ἡρῷον</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>μέτρον</el>), <i>an hexameter</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}